item.title: Prayer bpn6044 in Namibia
item.description: Mukuru wandje no muhona! owami omukarere wOye no muatje wo mukarere wOye. Mbapenduka motjirare tjandje me nyunguhuka ndi, tjandje Eyuva ndi rasana konyose ndji maimunikwa iyOuje auhe punga patyewa mo mambo wova Profete wOje, ngo tangwe Ove Mukuru wandje, twapendurwa Kondjerera jounongo wOye. Hinda kwete, Muhona wandje Oove erike ngu matutanga uriri Ndjipa owatjiri naimbo ovasuverwa vandje, ovazamumwe, ovarumendu poo ovakazendu, ovina oviwa vyOuje mbwi nOuje wo kombanda. Kara puna ete Muhona omuute wovina avihe vyOuje.
